    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_Lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: Alreightt
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _CurrentLines.Array.size
      value: 7
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[0]'
      value: "The Raymundo House, one of Malabon\u2019s oldest heritage houses that
        has been standing for years and even to this day."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[1]'
      value: "Built in the year 1861, the house was known for being constructed around
        the same time San Agustin Church was built, one of Malabon\u2019s notable
        monuments, and the same year our national hero, Jose Rizal was born."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[2]'
      value: "The house was home to Joe Raymundo with his wife Tina and their eight
        kids who all grew up adapting values and morals taught to them by their parents
        and their \u2018Nanang\u2019 in the Raymundo house."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[3]'
      value: Each member of the Raymundo family had their own stories created within
        the walls of the Raymundo home.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[4]'
      value: "This house has been a significant part of Malabon\u2019s heritage.
        It stands as a monument of history and cultural identity amongst the Malubenos."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[5]'
      value: The Raymundo house was always a haven and a place of friendship, where
        daily needs were met even in the most difficult circumstances by believers
        who knew the Lord would provide.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[6]'
      value: Unfortunately-
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
